            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.523809552192688,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "I always find myself coming back to play this game. Building up an empire and managing trade, your economy, alliances, public order, and armies is super satisfying. It always feels good to conquer a random enemy who had the audacity to declare war on you. Once you figure out the battles, they are a lot of fun to play. Overall, it is a great game, and I would highly recommend picking it up if you like strategy games."
        },
