            "review_text": "It's good. I played III first, but I think this one is still worth buying and playing at least a couple of campaigns. The vortex campaign is pretty nice; some races have better content in this game than in III (i.e. vampire coast). The game however seems harder slower paced than III and lacks some QoL improvements that were introduced in the sequel."
